2012-04-28 	Mario Campos	mcampos@mail.bradley.edu
	* implements a system call to convert the ascii mac address to hex.
	* implements proper system structures for ethernet addresses.

2012-04-27	Mario Campos	mcampos@mail.bradley.edu
	* released the first functional version of WOL.
	* supports MAC-48 addresses delimited by colons only.
	* includes two programs: a C-based program and a Perl-based script.
